flowchart TD
    A[Server includes CSP header\nin HTTP response\nContent-Security-Policy: default-src self] --> B[Browser parses CSP directives\ndefault-src, script-src, img-src, connect-src]
    B --> C[Page HTML loads\nand references resources]

    C --> D{Resource type: Script}
    D --> E{Script source\nmatches script-src allowlist?}
    E -- Yes, same origin or nonce match --> F[Script executes normally]
    E -- No, external or inline without nonce --> G[Browser blocks script\nlogs CSP violation]

    C --> H{Resource type: Image}
    H --> I{Image source\nmatches img-src allowlist?}
    I -- Yes --> J[Image loads normally]
    I -- No --> K[Browser blocks image load]

    C --> L{Resource type: Fetch/XHR}
    L --> M{Target URL\nmatches connect-src allowlist?}
    M -- Yes --> N[Request proceeds]
    M -- No --> O[Browser blocks network request]

    G --> P[Violation report sent\nto report-uri endpoint]
    K --> P
    O --> P
